    <section id="overview">
      <h2>Year Overview</h2>
      <p>The Tiger (<span class="chinese-char">虎</span>) occupies the Earthly Branch <strong>Yin (寅)</strong>, carrying Wood energy with hidden Fire and Earth. In 2026, the Tiger enjoys one of the most powerful harmonies in Chinese astrology: the <strong>Yin-Wu-Xu Fire Triangle</strong> (寅午戌三合火局). This San He (three harmony) combination with the Horse year creates an energetic alliance that amplifies both the Tiger's and the year's best qualities.</p>
      <p>Wood feeds Fire in the generating cycle, meaning the Tiger's energy naturally supports and is supported by the year's dominant element. This creates a sense of <strong>flow and momentum</strong> — doors open, people are receptive, and the Tiger's bold nature finds willing collaborators. 2026 is a year to take action on ambitions that have been developing quietly.</p>
      <p>The Bing (丙) Heavenly Stem shines a spotlight on the Tiger's leadership abilities. Visibility is high, and public-facing activities are favoured. The Tiger's natural magnetism is amplified — use this influence wisely.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="career">
      <h2>Career &amp; Finance</h2>
      <p>The fire triangle creates <strong>outstanding career momentum</strong>. The Tiger is recognised, promoted, and given increasing responsibility. Leadership roles suit perfectly — whether launching a business, heading a team, or taking on public-facing positions. The year rewards courage and initiative.</p>
      <p><strong>Finance</strong> is generally strong, with income growth supported by career advancement. However, the Wood-Fire dynamic means the Tiger's resources are actively being consumed to fuel achievement. Budget carefully despite growing income — expenses naturally rise to match new status and obligations.</p>
      <p><strong>Best sectors:</strong> Entertainment, media, public relations, politics, education, and creative industries. Any field requiring charisma, vision, and bold decision-making is aligned with the Tiger's 2026 energy.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="love">
      <h2>Love &amp; Relationships</h2>
      <p>Fire's passionate energy makes 2026 a <strong>romantically vibrant year</strong>. The Tiger's attractiveness is at a peak, drawing attention and admiration. Existing relationships deepen through shared adventures and mutual support of ambitious goals.</p>
      <p><strong>Single Tigers</strong> have excellent prospects. The fire triangle's warmth and energy attract compatible partners — especially those born in Horse or Dog years (completing the triangle). Romance that begins during the spring or autumn months has strong long-term potential.</p>
      <p><strong>Caution:</strong> The same intensity that fuels passion can create jealousy or possessiveness. The Tiger must balance personal ambition with relationship investment — partners who feel sidelined by the Tiger's career drive may express frustration.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="health">
      <h2>Health &amp; Wellness</h2>
      <p>The primary health concern for Tigers in 2026 is <strong>burnout and exhaustion</strong>. Wood feeding Fire is a powerful but draining dynamic — the Tiger is literally fuelling the year's energy from personal reserves. Without conscious rest and recovery, the second half of the year may see energy depletion.</p>
      <p><strong>Liver health</strong> (Wood's organ) needs attention. Moderate alcohol consumption, manage anger and frustration, and ensure adequate sleep. The Tiger's tendency to push through fatigue must be checked.</p>
      <p><strong>Exercise</strong> should be vigorous but balanced with recovery. Competitive sports satisfy the Tiger's nature, but pair them with restorative practices — massage, sauna, or gentle stretching. Hydration is especially important as Fire energy depletes fluids.</p>
    </section>

